    ('ENG-L 295', 'AMERICAN FILM CULTURE', '13067', 'Closed', NULL, 'WB WEB', 'De Witt Kilgore', 0, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'WEB-BASED CLASS', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Film in relation to American culture and society. Topic varies. Works of literature may be used for comparison but the main emphasis will be on film as a narrative medium and as an important element in American culture.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd A&H credit
