    ('FRIT-F 435', 'ENLIGHTENMENT NARRATIVE', '30307', 'Class Status', 'TuTh Tuesday, Thursday 11:10 AM–12:25 PM', 'LH 016', 'Guillaume Ansart', 2, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'LINDLEY HALL', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Narratives in the form of letters, memoirs, dialogues, and tales. Writers such as Marivaux, Prevost, Voltaire, Diderot, Mme de Charriare, Constant, Chateaubriand. Social, political, and cultural interchange between the writer and his/her world, from classicism to romanticism.', ARRAY['COLL (CASE) A&H Breadth of Inquiry credit'], NULL)
